Description.Text: The property offers a very good level of quality and service with easy access to all main sights and places of interest within the city. MW0906
Situated in the centre of Moscow within easy proximity of the main attractions and not far from Belorusskaya metro station

The rooms are a good size, with all the facilities one would expect from a this kind of product. The rooms are decorated in soft pastel colours with light wooden furniture. The bathrooms are also in very good condition.
The modern building fits in nicely with the neighbourhood. The concrete facade is topped by steel and glass window frames.

There are 3 restaurants in total and the main one "La Terazza" is located on the first floor. It is expansive, with a light and airy atmosphere and offers a mix of international cuisine. There is also the Mozart cafe and the lobby bar.

The small lobby is brightly lit with large shop front windows. The entrance is from a sidestreet. The reception area is situated to the right of the door and to the left are the lifts and an expansive bar area.
